                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h4>How many IF units do I need to pass to complete the CII Certificate in Insurance?</h4>
                    <p>The number of units depends on whether you are pursuing the Award (minimum one unit at 15 credits) or the Certificate (minimum two units meeting the CII's current credit threshold). Most students working toward the Certificate complete two to four IF units depending on employer requirements. This service covers any combination of IF units from IF1 through IF11, GR1, LM3, R05, and all seven international variants.</p>
